#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/main/guides/security-jwt.adoc:22
msgid "Quarkus OpenID Connect `quarkus-oidc` extension also supports Bearer Token Authorization and uses `smallrye-jwt` to represent the bearer tokens as `JsonWebToken`.  For more information, read the xref:security-oidc-bearer-authentication-concept.adoc[OIDC Bearer authentication] guide.  OpenID Connect extension has to be used if the Quarkus application needs to authenticate the users using OIDC Authorization Code Flow.  For more information, see xref:security-oidc-code-flow-authentication-concept.adoc[OIDC code flow mechanism for protecting web applications]"
